{
  "texts": [
    "We believe that the key to unlocking this potential lies not in large-scale human annotation but in the provision of hard reasoning questions, a reliable verifier and sufficient computational resources for RL.",
    "Sophisticated reasoning behaviours, such as self-verification and reflection, seemed to emerge organically during the RL process.",
    "Even if DeepSeek-R1 achieves frontier results on reasoning benchmarks, it still faces several capability limitations, as outlined below.",
    "At present, the structural output capabilities of DeepSeek-R1 remain suboptimal compared with existing models.",
    "Moreover, DeepSeek-R1 cannot make use of tools, such as search engines and calculators, to improve the performance of output."
  ]
}